HONG KONG , August 18 -LRB- Xinhua -RRB- -- The troops of the Chinese People 's Liberation Army stationed in Hong Kong have donated an additional 618,671 yuan -LRB- about 74,540 U.S. dollars -RRB- to the flood victims in the Chinese mainland , it is learned here Tuesday .
So far the donations of the PLA troops in Hong Kong have accumulated to 1.6 million yuan -LRB- 0.19 million U.S. dollars -RRB- in response to a call of the PLA headquarters to help the flood victims .
